PubChem Fu: PubChem Utilities

Prerequisites:

- Ruby (http://ruby-lang.org)
- Ruby Gems (http://rubygems.org/pages/download)
- Whenever gem (http://github.com/javan/whenever)

Create a full copy of PubChem (in the same directory as PubChem Fu):

$ rake full

Pull available daily updates (in the same directory as PubChem Fu):

$ rake daily

Automate pulling daily updates:

$ whenever --update-crontab pubchem

Make sure your cron task is set:

$ crontab -l

Resources:

For a nice tutorial on using Ruby and Whenever to control cron, see:

http://media.railscasts.com/videos/164_cron_in_ruby.mov

